 and email campaigns — through an event-driven architecture. The system integrates with Vapi (voice/chat API), Make (automation webhooks), OpenAI assistants, and includes a full admin dashboard for analytics, mailing, security operations, user management, and server maintenance. The codebase has 20+ god components (largest: AdminMailingPage at 4519 lines, AdminBackupsPage at 4381 lines) indicating significant technical debt through monolithic components. Key risk areas: the analytics overview route (309 dependents), the Vapi chat POST handler (complexity 136), and the chat route (complexity 47). No unit or integration tests were found in the repository. Authentication supports password + TOTP MFA with trusted devices, and the system uses Prisma for data persistence with a rich schema covering Users, Visitors, Calls, ChatSessions, Leads, Campaigns, Mailing templates/campaigns/audiences, and SyncJobs.\"\n```",
